<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش ن ق:</span> <span class="c2">(الشَّنَقُ)</span> فِي الصَّدَقَةِ مَا بَيْنَ الْفَرِيضَتَيْنِ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا شِنَاقَ»</span> أَيْ لَا يُؤْخَذُ مِنَ الشَّنَقِ حَتَّى تَتِمَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>